  <p class="text-muted">The Taj Mahal is widely considered one of the most beautiful buildings ever created.
    The exquisite marble structure in Agra, India, is a mausoleum, an enduring monument to the love of a husband for his favorite wife.
    It's also an eternal testament to the artistic and scientific accomplishments of a wealthy empire.</p>
